{"tid":2146213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"放棄台大讀私立　2名高中生領360萬元獎學金！","createTime":"2020-08-08T12:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T06:17:42.000Z","uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc740cb084a10a167b9cf42047abdafc8288ee03","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5059/d5059050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5059%2Fd5059050.jpg&h=db5cdd86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學指考分發入學昨（7）日放榜，今年整體錄取率91.14%，創校19年的亞洲大學錄取率達102.13%。特別的是，有2名北市高中學生採計科目分數在全國前3%內，最終放棄台大，第一志願改填亞大，將能領到360萬元獎學金。<br />\n<br />\n亞大主任秘書兼招生處長施能義表示，可領360萬元的高姓學生，是台北市復興高中畢業，原本可進台灣大學，第一志願卻選擇亞大生物資訊暨醫學工程系（生醫資訊組）就讀。另位吳姓同學，畢業於政大附中，也高分選擇就讀亞大財經法律系（科技法律組）。"},{"pid":"a08980077efabf91842189ec368740d3f12e8dc7","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"他們的分數都在採計科目<span class=\"red\">全國前3%內</span>，加上第一志願選擇亞大，符合亞大新生入學最高獎金條件，初估可領取360萬元入學獎學金，<span class=\"red\">至今僅有5人獲得最高額獎金</span>。<br />\n<br />\n施能義主任秘書說，亞大提供新生入學獎學金最高可領360萬元，外加海外雙聯碩士、雙聯博士助學獎金最高120萬元，合計可領480萬元；過去8年，亞大除了發給3位領360萬元的資優生外，陸續核發100萬元、20萬元、8萬元及英文成績優良、AI人才培育等獎學金等，迄今共核發6176萬元。"},{"pid":"b14b708179bcb2645cfcd8b875a9803474475d22","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"香港100萬讀HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b334d9fd6d2e8a4863abbfce1229a7d02a51f8","tid":2146213,"uid":193290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"葉亞台清交"},{"pid":"0a9f942664ed240c98683f1a0f4c8dcf56899e47","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=793620&amp;fbclid=IwAR0JMFjqj3xlejsTAoQBrUo62kgUay0t2_2PCsYmPtt_vFX4wx8NRW4dO88</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bdb4bb4031424526c9f766fad0f0480697f88268","tid":2146213,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"大學指考分發入學昨（7）日放榜<br />\n<br />\n淨係第一句都睇左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a92edd679df5b5c796f2f42499e46628baea56b","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"錄取率達102.13%係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6802c7dcfa4e86eef75236a9d15b97e9b2d2b105","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"含大要唔要試下 <br />\n25分揀含大有獎學金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283759fe44caf5eb3643d7d49489547b8863409c","tid":2146213,"uid":105490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a92edd679df5b5c796f2f42499e46628baea56b","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"錄取率達102.13%係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"係人都讀得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地畢業前 就已經比人地先賺左錢10年人工<br />\n再讀埋咩雙學位就接近超越人地15年"},{"pid":"90434ddc3e140ab966634760b1f8f4a1d658e97c","tid":2146213,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a92edd679df5b5c796f2f42499e46628baea56b","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"錄取率達102.13%係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"超額收生？"},{"pid":"cc59ebfb01550c3c8a3b7cce7b2939714eeafde6","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"283759fe44caf5eb3643d7d49489547b8863409c","tid":2146213,"uid":105490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a92edd679df5b5c796f2f42499e46628baea56b","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"錄取率達102.13%係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"係人都讀得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地畢業前 就已經比人地先賺左錢10年人工<br />\n再讀埋咩雙學位就接近超越人地15年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算唔算係明智"},{"pid":"bb54018504d9e5bafdd6828a63e8b7cc7caa2f95","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"btw,間大學都幾靚"},{"pid":"83b926985f6800d69095ca79e585b9c9f747f0eb","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"如果含大有50萬我都讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775ad5d1b908fa8bb4d0f8022b8b3c7e69267610","tid":2146213,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"幾好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁可唔可以再私底下報返台大，兩間大學一齊返<br />\n咁又有錢又有名"},{"pid":"93df08c18b44515819f1bee531fc8c99a6433408","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775ad5d1b908fa8bb4d0f8022b8b3c7e69267610","tid":2146213,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"幾好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁可唔可以再私底下報返台大，兩間大學一齊返<br />\n咁又有錢又有名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"應該唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dbf6dd4eab46eb3e0ecf5e6cbd2fbeac21b7a3","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"原PO在PTT發文表示，自稱是領了獎學金的其中一名學生，因為網路上有許多人在討論此事，因此她特別PO文澄清。她表示自己捨棄台大畢業證書，並不會覺得可惜，因為她的數乙分數不佳，就算要上台大，也只能選擇不採計數學的人類和歷史系。但又因為她沒有考英聽，也沒有考學測數學，所以也和這2科系斷了緣分，嚴格來說她是沒辦法上台大的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n關於未來畢業出路，原PO則說，自己未來想考國考，但目標沒有放在司法官、律師這麼大，且就算是台大畢業的人，也同樣會選擇去補習，所以她選擇亞大賺取獎學金，讓補習班的學費有著落，她認為這也不是壞事。"},{"pid":"be1ede433a69c7ec84d233a363c39a203269c4db","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"不讀台大是否等同於捨棄人脈，原PO也有自己的見解，表示就算就讀台大，也不是想抱人大腿就可以的，且她自認為不擅社交，即使進了台大，也可能會變成邊緣人。若真心想要結交人脈，她認為參加NGO、研討會或是去參加教育營等活動也可以發展。至於之後碩士要不要考回台大，她表示若應屆考上國考，就不考慮碩士了，不過如果沒有考上，則可以拚拚看。<br />\n<br />\n也有人好奇，她是不是因為缺錢才會選擇有360萬獎學金的亞洲大學，原PO表示，自己家中並不缺錢，也沒有出國計畫，因為英文不夠好。是否要用這筆錢來投資，她則說自己不排除這個做法，但她還沒開始研究，預計明後年才會開始。最後她也說，關於網友傳言的買跑車找妹子，表示「我是女生啦，雖然不排斥百合，但是網友的那種幻想真的好噁心」。"},{"pid":"b0061112848c1072efd15afe144f84eb7fefc065","tid":2146213,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc59ebfb01550c3c8a3b7cce7b2939714eeafde6","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"283759fe44caf5eb3643d7d49489547b8863409c","tid":2146213,"uid":105490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a92edd679df5b5c796f2f42499e46628baea56b","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"錄取率達102.13%係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"係人都讀得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地畢業前 就已經比人地先賺左錢10年人工<br />\n再讀埋咩雙學位就接近超越人地15年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算唔算係明智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"緊係明智啦<br />\n根本拎個幾百萬去投資<br />\n人地一畢業<br />\n佢地呢幾年投資賺既錢已經夠退休<br />\n洗撚做野咩"},{"pid":"a7e55f8439cf1aa7daa847bbf9e76ec11f25fcdd","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"入唔到台大都有得拎360萬咁都幾抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾醒目"},{"pid":"3630d53c6be47bf34804c4482b8f722460f3dd29","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0061112848c1072efd15afe144f84eb7fefc065","tid":2146213,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc59ebfb01550c3c8a3b7cce7b2939714eeafde6","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"283759fe44caf5eb3643d7d49489547b8863409c","tid":2146213,"uid":105490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"係人都讀得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地畢業前 就已經比人地先賺左錢10年人工<br />\n再讀埋咩雙學位就接近超越人地15年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算唔算係明智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"緊係明智啦<br />\n根本拎個幾百萬去投資<br />\n人地一畢業<br />\n佢地呢幾年投資賺既錢已經夠退休<br />\n洗撚做野咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"都要投資成功既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6802c7dcfa4e86eef75236a9d15b97e9b2d2b105","tid":2146213,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"含大要唔要試下 <br />\n25分揀含大有獎學金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}